data.description: This charming 3-bedroom ranch is nestled in the heart of Romulus. As you enter, you'll be greeted by the warmth of the recently installed furnace, ensuring your winters are cozy and energy-efficient. The brand-new central AC unit promises refreshing coolness during the warmer months. A new water heater adds to the list of upgrades. The exterior includes a new privacy fence to enjoy outdoor activities with family and friends. The canopy on the patio is included. Inside, the kitchen and family room have new flooring. The new door wall leading to the back patio seamlessly connects indoor and outdoor living. House Generator and Appliances included. New front window. Immediate Occupancy. Don't miss the opportunity to make this meticulously updated property your own. As-Is Sale.
